metadata.description: Dose embryos from MOH library plate with  <50 ul per well. Use intermediate plate to dilute MOH stock + PSC into FSW before applying to embryos. Dose embryos with 50ul of 4X MOH + PSC in FSW intermediate. Added pause before embryo dosing.
